Package: DoseFindingExtra
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Theodoros", "Papathanasiou", , "theo.x.papathanasiou@gsk.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Tools to simulate dose-response studies and evaluate target dose estimation
    accuracy, posterior-based power, and go/no-go decision logic under uncertainty. Includes
    support for multiple model types (e.g., Emax, sigEmax, quadratic) and clinical thresholds.
